		left join (
			SELECT aa.wave_no,SUM(IFNULL(aa.items_num,0)) AS items_num FROM u13123456789_tid_orders aa 
			INNER JOIN (SELECT new_tid FROM u13123456789_wave_list ) AS bb ON bb.new_tid=aa.new_tid 
			GROUP BY aa.wave_no
		) as c on c.wave_no=a.wave_no
		left join (select wh,name as wh_name from u13123456789_my_wh) as d on d.wh=a.wh
		 where  1=1 group by a.wave_no limit 0,10
